Good evening, I'm receiving unfair reviews, I lower my grade a lot, when I perfectly execute the mechanical utilities and function of my class, of a tank who dies in boss mechanics, of a healer who can't heal in basic AoE mechanics from DG (even though I'm using defensive) I would like to know what to do about this, and if this system is so unfair why don't you just remove these reviews?
I think you can file an appeal if you think the reviews are bad

What happens is that when the DG does well, I don't receive an evaluation, when the DG doesn't do so well, and through no fault of my own, I receive a bad evaluation, so how much does this really help?
Maybe forcing everyone to evaluate everything could create a balance
That happens to everyone, the best thing would be to try to mark in a group of friends
The reviews are personal and are not obligatory to place.... what they do a lot is "exchange" the reviews ..for example: you give me a 10/10 review, I do the same with you.
But everyone has the right to place any score from 0 to 10, as long as it is respectfully ...without insults, racist-homophobic comments, etc

If you don't like a review that you have been placed (low score) ,you can appeal for it ...you need 10 votes from people , and if you have premium , you can appeal with the premium mode, which is reviewed by the admins (this last mode is easier , because you only need the approval of 1 admin)
